---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const base = '/GoswickRanchMayerArizona';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Location & Directions — Goswick Ranch HOA"
  description="Directions to Goswick Ranch near Mayer, Arizona from Prescott and Phoenix."
  pageTitle="Location & Directions"
  pageSubtitle="S Goswick Ranch Rd, Mayer, AZ 86333"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { label: 'Home', href: `${base}/` },
    { label: 'About', href: `${base}/about/` },
    { label: 'Location & Directions' }
  ]}
>
  <div class="page-content">

    <div class="map-container">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.openstreetmap.org/export/embed.html?bbox=-112.28%2C34.37%2C-112.14%2C34.47&amp;layer=mapnik&amp;marker=34.4016%2C-112.2312"
        width="100%" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"
        title="Map of Mayer, Arizona">
      </iframe>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-2);">
      Map data &copy; <a href="https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright" target="_blank" rel="noopener">OpenStreetMap</a> contributors.
    </p>

    <div class="prose" style="margin-top: var(--space-8);">

      <h2>Directions</h2>

      <h3>From Prescott via SR-69</h3>
      <p>Head east on AZ-69 (State Route 69) from Prescott through Dewey-Humboldt toward Mayer — approximately 27 miles. Once through the Mayer townsite, turn south (right) onto <strong>E Poland Rd</strong> (also shown as Poland Junction Rd). Follow Poland Rd to <strong>S Goswick Ranch Rd</strong> and turn south. The gated entrance will be on your right.</p>

      <h3>From Phoenix via I-17</h3>
      <p>Take I-17 north to <strong>Exit 262</strong> (Cordes Junction / Mayer). Head northwest on Cordes Junction Road to AZ-69, then turn north and continue approximately 8 miles through Cordes Lakes to the Mayer area. Turn west (left) onto <strong>E Poland Rd</strong> (Poland Junction Rd). Follow Poland Rd to <strong>S Goswick Ranch Rd</strong> and look for the gated entrance.</p>

      <div class="notice notice-warn">
        <p><strong>Gate access:</strong> Goswick Ranch is a gated community. Residents are responsible for providing gate access to guests and vendors. Contact the board via the <a href={`${base}/contact/`}>contact form</a> for access questions.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Nearby Points of Reference</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Destination</th><th>Distance</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Mayer, AZ (town center)</td><td>~2 miles</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Prescott, AZ</td><td>~27 miles</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Cordes Junction (I-17 Exit 262)</td><td>~15 miles</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Prescott Valley</td><td>~20 miles</td></tr>
          <tr><td>North Phoenix suburbs</td><td>~40 miles</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Prescott Airport (PRC)</td><td>~28 miles</td></tr>
          <tr><td>YRMC Hospital (Prescott Valley)</td><td>~13 miles</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
